[
  {
    "text": "I'm Clint Smith and this is\n\"Ode to the Only Black Kid in the Class.\"",
    "start": 1.815,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "You, it seems,\nare the manifestation",
    "start": 8.206,
    "duration": 3.05
  },
  {
    "text": "of several lifetimes\nof toil.",
    "start": 11.256,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Brown v. Board\nin flesh.",
    "start": 13.826,
    "duration": 2.239
  },
  {
    "text": "Most days\nthe classroom feels",
    "start": 16.065,
    "duration": 1.761
  },
  {
    "text": "like an antechamber.",
    "start": 17.826,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "You are deemed expert",
    "start": 19.386,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "on all things Morrison,\nKing, Malcolm, Rosa.",
    "start": 20.646,
    "duration": 5.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Hell, weren’t you sitting\non that bus, too?",
    "start": 25.756,
    "duration": 2.69
  },
  {
    "text": "You are every-\nbody’s best friend",
    "start": 28.446,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "until you are not.",
    "start": 30.106,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Hip-hop lyricologist.",
    "start": 31.796,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Presumed athlete.",
    "start": 33.236,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Free & Reduced sideshow.",
    "start": 34.896,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Exception and caricature.",
    "start": 36.496,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Too black and too white\nall at once.",
    "start": 38.576,
    "duration": 2.65
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are successful",
    "start": 41.226,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "it is because\nof affirmative action.",
    "start": 42.466,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "If you fail it is because",
    "start": 44.666,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "you were destined to.",
    "start": 46.146,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "You are invisible until they turn on\nthe Friday night lights.",
    "start": 47.836,
    "duration": 3.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Here you are star before\nthey render you asteroid.",
    "start": 51.466,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Before they watch\nyou turn to dust.",
    "start": 54.406,
    "duration": 3.19
  }
]